title: Did not receive my sytery champion for ocean week.
body: hey, i got over 4 points for ocean week and was wondering if there was something else i needed to get the free champion. Thanks for the support

replies.body:
Hey there,

The mystery champions are still currently being rolled out, this is being done in batches and should be completed by the end of the week.

If you're yet to receive yours just wait it out, patience is key :)
